                        <div class="col">
                            <h3>Health rate system</h3>
                            <p>Healthy sleep is not just the number of hours spent in bed, but also a discipline
                                with bio-logic, and necessary adherence to a regime. All core systems in Dormint
                                take a holistic approach to monitor and help the user reach their goals. The Health
                                rate indicator aims to mimic this complexity and affects the number of tokens that
                                are earned. It is established with the aid of microphone and (optional) health
                                sensor data. The user will simply inform the application by indicating the beginning
                                and end of his Sleep cycle and the app will do the rest.</p>
                            <div class="text-box">
                                <p>The Health rate is affected by three main multipliers:</p>
