                            <p>A user starts out with the optimal Health rate value, which may go down depending on
                                how much they violate their sleep regime, with the worst offences completely
                                disabling the earnings for that Sleep cycle.</p>
                            <p>Negative effects and Penalties are the first multipliers that are applied to a user’s
                                Health rate and have a greater effect than Boosters. The newly modified Health Rate
                                remains and affects the next Sleep cycle after which it is reassessed.</p>
